  "name": "Compass and Board Orientation Configuration",
  "description": "You are an agricultural technician commissioning a custom crop-dusting drone. The autopilot board is mounted rotated 90° clockwise (Yaw90) and the external GPS/compass is mounted 180° from standard (Yaw180). The internal compasses must be disabled due to electromagnetic interference from the spray pump motor. Configure the following 8 parameters in QGroundControl using the values specified in /home/ga/Documents/QGC/mounting_spec.txt: AHRS_ORIENTATION, COMPASS_ORIENT, COMPASS_EXTERNAL, COMPASS_USE2, COMPASS_USE3, COMPASS_LEARN, COMPASS_OFS_X, and COMPASS_OFS_Y.",
